flowchart TD
    Q[1. User question] --> SCHEMA[2. Load schema (sqlite.py)]
    SCHEMA --> GR[3. GuardrailsAgent.evaluate]

    GR -->|OUT OF SCOPE| OOS[Return OUT_OF_SCOPE message]
    GR -->|NEEDS CLARIFICATION| CLAR[Return CLARIFY question]
    GR -->|READY_FOR_SQL| SQL[4. SQLAgent.generate_sql]

    SQL --> VAL[5. validate_sql]
    VAL -->|invalid| REPAIR[ErrorAgent.repair_sql]
    VAL -->|valid| EXEC[6. execute_sql]

    EXEC -->|execution error| REPAIR
    REPAIR --> RETRY{Retry left?}
    RETRY -->|yes| VAL
    RETRY -->|no| FAIL[Return ERROR (max retries)]

    EXEC -->|success| FORMAT[7. format_response]
    FORMAT --> ANALYSIS[8. AnalysisAgent.summarize]
    ANALYSIS --> VIZ[9. VizAgent.generate\nfallback: viz_plotly]
    VIZ --> DONE[10. Return final payload]
